<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA69">
<l>akañcivanta kaṇṇiṉarāy valviṉaiya rāvār</l>
<l>mukañcitaiva rāmaṉṟē mukki mikuntirumāl</l>
<l>cīrkkaṭalai yuḷpotinta cintaṉaiyēṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>yārkkaṭalāñ cevvē yaṭarttu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] harsh deeds have become such as whose eyes have reddened inside,</l>
<l>it is that [their] faces decay, isn’t it?, strained. Me with thoughts</l>
<l>that are stored in the ocean of excellence of increasing Tirumāl,</l>
<l>for whom is there straight oppressing [and] killing me?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
